WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.458 --> 00:00:01.710
Modern work is top of mind

2
00:00:01.710 --> 00:00:03.086
for us here at surface.

3
00:00:03.086 --> 00:00:03.670
And we're excited

4
00:00:03.670 --> 00:00:04.546
to present our newest

5
00:00:04.546 --> 00:00:06.339
edition of Surface Laptop

6
00:00:06.339 --> 00:00:07.757
with an optional integrated

7
00:00:07.757 --> 00:00:08.675
privacy screen

8
00:00:08.675 --> 00:00:10.093
and anti-glare display

9
00:00:10.093 --> 00:00:12.178
on our 13.8in model.

10
00:00:12.178 --> 00:00:13.722
Ideal for mobile professionals

11
00:00:13.722 --> 00:00:15.557
who work in public spaces.

12
00:00:15.557 --> 00:00:17.017
Users can work confidently

13
00:00:17.017 --> 00:00:18.685
and privately while still preserving

14
00:00:18.685 --> 00:00:20.353
touch responsiveness

15
00:00:20.353 --> 00:00:21.479
and our signature high

16
00:00:21.479 --> 00:00:22.814
quality Pixelsense flow

17
00:00:22.814 --> 00:00:25.817
display with a 120Hz refresh rate

18
00:00:25.859 --> 00:00:26.818
providing clarity

19
00:00:26.818 --> 00:00:27.861
in almost any light

20
00:00:27.861 --> 00:00:30.864
with HDR and 600 nits of brightness.

21
00:00:30.905 --> 00:00:31.781
This is for users

22
00:00:31.781 --> 00:00:33.283
who prioritize portability

23
00:00:33.283 --> 00:00:34.993
and visual privacy

24
00:00:34.993 --> 00:00:36.494
for users who work in open

25
00:00:36.494 --> 00:00:39.456
offices, shared spaces, or on the move

26
00:00:39.664 --> 00:00:41.916
with the press of one dedicated key.

27
00:00:41.916 --> 00:00:44.127
The screen dims to significantly reduce

28
00:00:44.127 --> 00:00:45.336
on screen visibility

29
00:00:45.336 --> 00:00:46.546
