40
00:01:04.022 --> 00:01:04.731
This new feature

41
00:01:04.731 --> 00:01:05.648
is a direct result

42
00:01:05.648 --> 00:01:06.816
of surface's commitment

43
00:01:06.816 --> 00:01:08.735
to premium craftsmanship,

44
00:01:08.735 --> 00:01:10.528
a depiction of meticulously designed

45
00:01:10.528 --> 00:01:12.781
hardware to empower your productivity

46
00:01:12.781 --> 00:01:15.200
and keep you in the flow of your work.

47
00:01:15.200 --> 00:01:16.326
Availability of Surface

48
00:01:16.326 --> 00:01:17.285
Laptop's integrated

49
00:01:17.285 --> 00:01:19.412
privacy screen with anti-glare varies

50
00:01:19.412 --> 00:01:21.623
